 enhanced safety and awareness.<\/p><p><span class=\"highlight\">Key Features<\/span><\/p><ul><li><strong>Bone Conduction Technology:<\/strong> Provides premium sound quality while minimizing ear canal damage and reducing infection risks. ENT-certified for extended, safe use.<\/li><li><strong>Lightweight Design:<\/strong> Weighs just 35 grams for ultimate comfort during active use.<\/li><li><strong>IP68 Waterproof Rating:<\/strong> Perfect for swimming, jogging, gym workouts, and other intense activities.<\/li><li><strong>Dual ENC Microphones:<\/strong> Ensures crystal-clear calls even in noisy environments.<\/li><li><strong>8GB Onboard Storage:<\/strong> Holds up to 1,000 songs for phone-free listening convenience.<\/li><li><strong>Hearing Aid Functionality:<\/strong> A practical option for individuals with hearing impairments.<\/li><\/ul><p><span class=\"highlight\">Versatility and Innovation<\/span><br>Whether you're looking for sports headphones, running headphones, or swimming earphones, these open-ear headphones redefine versatility with comfort and cutting-edge functionality.<\/p><p><span class=\"highlight\">Peace of Mind<\/span><\/p><ul><li><strong>Free Shipping<\/strong><\/li><li><strong>7-Day Return Policy<\/strong><\/li><li><strong>1-Year Replacement Warranty with At-Home Service<\/strong><\/li><\/ul><p><span><strong>Order Now<\/strong><\/span><br>Upgrade your audio experience with NG EarSafe Pro Open Ear Bone Conduction Headphones. Buy now and embrace the future of listening!<\/p><\/div><\/div><style>.accordion{width:450px;border:1px solid #ddd;border-radius:5px;overflow:hidden;margin-bottom:15px}.accordion input{display:none}.accordion-label{display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:center;padding:5px 20px;color:#252525;cursor:pointer;font-size:15px;font-weight:600;transition:background-color .3s ease}.accordion-label::after{content:'▼';font-size:16px;transition:transform .3s ease}.accordion input:checked+.accordion-label::after{transform:r