ading":"","text":"<h4><br\/>Trending Searches By Readers<strong><br\/><\/strong><\/h4><p><\/p><p><a href=\"https:\/\/ngearsafe.com\/blogs\/open-ear-headphones\/headphone-for-glasses-wearers\">Best Headphones For Glasses<\/a> | <a href=\"https:\/\/ngearsafe.com\/blogs\/open-ear-headphones\/bone-conduction-headphones-side-effects\">Bone Conduction Headphones Safe<\/a> | <a href=\"https:\/\/ngearsafe.com\/products\/ng-earsafe-comm-open-ear-headphones-with-noise-canceling-boom-mic\">Office Headsets<\/a> | <a href=\"https:\/\/ngearsafe.com\/blogs\/open-ear-headphones\/headphones-for-meditation-the-new-way-to-relax-and-focus\">Best Headphones For Meditation<\/a> | <a href=\"https:\/\/ngearsafe.com\/pages\/bone-conduction\">How Do Bone Conduction Headphones Work<\/a> | <a href=\"https:\/\/ngearsafe.com\/collections\/open-ear-headphones\">Bluetooth Safety Headphones<\/a> | <a href=\"https:\/\/ngearsafe.com\/products\/ng-earsafe-openbuds-with-air-conduction-technology\">Safety Earbuds<\/a> | <a href=\"https:\/\/ngearsafe.com\/products\/ng-earsafe-lite-open-ear-headphones\">Neckband Headphones Bluetooth<\/a> | <a href=\"https:\/\/ngearsafe.com\/pages\/air-conduction\">Best Headphones To Avoid Ear Infections<\/a> | <a href=\"https:\/\/ngearsafe.com\/pages\/bulk-orders\">Wholesale Headphones<\/a><a href=\"https:\/\/ngearsafe.com\/collections\/open-ear-headphones\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https:\/\/ngearsafe.com\/collections\/open-ear-headphones\"><br\/><br\/><\/a><\/p>","subhd_color":"#222222","hd_color":"#222222","des_color":"#878787","use_shadow":false,"button_label":"Button label","button_link":"","open_link":"_blank","btn_icon":false,"button_style":"default","btn_size":"large","btn_cl":"dark","button_effect":"default"}}},"block_order":["bl_text_y8bTHf"],"custom_css":[".t4s-image-text-des p a {color: #25313c; border-bottom: 1px solid #25313c45 !important; font-size: 14px;}"],"settings":{"design_heading":"1","heading_align":"t4s-text-start","top_heading":"","icon_heading":"las la-gem","top_subheading":"","tophead_mb":30,"space_h_item":"20","space_v_item":"10","space_h_item_mb":"20","space_v_item_mb":"10","layout":"t4s-container-wrap","cl_bg":"","cl_bg_gradient":"","mg":",,50px,","pd":"","mg_tb":"","pd_tb":"","mg_mb":",,30px,","pd_mb":"","use_cus_css":false,"code_cus_css":""}},"custom_html_Hr3UiD":{"type":"custom-html","settings":{"code":"<div class=\"t4s-text-center\" style=\"padding: 15px 0;color: #fff;\">\n    <div class=\"footer-seo\">\n        <h2>NG EarSafe Pro Open Ear Bone Conduction Headphones: Safe Listening with Premium Sound<\/h2>\n        \n        <h3>Bone Conduction Technology for Safety<\/h3>\n        <p>\n            Designed for those who prioritize ear health and situational awareness, the NG EarSafe Pro Open Ear Bone Conduction Headphones offer a groundbreaking audio experience. Utilizing advanced <strong>bone conduction technology<\/strong>, these headphones transmit sound through vibrations along your cheekbones, bypassing the eardrum to deliver crisp, high-quality audio directly to your inner ear. This keeps your ear canals open, letting you hear ambient sounds like approaching footsteps or honking horns. Whether you’re running on a trail, cycling through the city, or simply relaxing outdoors, you stay fully aware of your surroundings without missing a beat.\n        <\/p>\n        \n        <h3>Lightweight Comfort and Waterproof Durability<\/h3>\n        <p>\n            Weighing just 35 grams, the <strong>lightweight and ergonomic design<\/strong> of the NG EarSafe Pro ensures a snug, comfortable fit for all-day wear. Picture yourself powering through a sweaty gym session, swimming laps in the pool, or jogging in the rain. These headphones, with their <strong>IP68 waterproof rating<\/strong>, thrive in any condition, resisting water, sweat, and dust with ease. The flexible frame adapts to your movements, staying secure during intense activities. With an <strong>8-hour battery life<\/strong> and a quick 1-hour charge via magnetic connection, you’ll enjoy uninterrupted listening from morning workouts to evening wind-downs.\n        <\/p>\n        \n        <h3>Versatile Features and Crystal-Clear Calls<\/h3>\n        <p>\n            Equipped with <strong>Bluetooth 5.3<\/strong>, the NG EarSafe Pro provides a stable, fast connection up to 33 feet, perfect for pairing with your phone or smartwatch. The built-in <strong>dual ENC microphones<\/strong> filter out background noise, ensuring your voice comes through loud and clear during calls, even in windy or crowded settings. For phone-free convenience, the <strong>8GB onboard storage<\/strong> holds up to 1,000 songs, letting you enjoy music, podcasts, or audiobooks without extra devices. Available in Black and Blue, these headphones also double as a hearing aid solution for those with conductive hearing loss. From sports enthusiasts to professionals, the NG EarSafe Pro blends safety, style, and superior sound. Redefine your audio experience today!\n        <\/p>\n    <\/div>\n<\/div>\n\n<style>\n    .footer-seo {color:#ddd;padding:30px;text-align:left;border-radius:8px}\n    .footer-seo h2 {color:#fff;font-size:16px;margin-bottom:15px;text-align:left}\n    .footer-seo h3 {color:#fff;font-size:14px;margin-bottom:10px;text-align:left}\n    .footer-seo p {font-size:14px;line-height:1.6}\n<\/style>","layout":"t4s-container-fluid","cl_bg":"#252525","cl_bg_gradient":"","mg":",,0px,","pd":"","mg_tb":"","pd_tb":"","mg_mb":",,0px,","pd_mb":"","use_cus_css":false,"code_cus_css":""}}},"order":["custom_liquid_YfCYJ9","breadcrumb","main","1737396661bce966ef","slideshow_AdjaCJ","sidebar","21cc52cf-8bcf-42ba-8f07-80d94e7a589e","617310e4-15e9-4543-82e0-1f050ae4ab1e","top_heading_p6MtX8","601092f3-f61a-4147-b4f4-33b069d7f348","a0e3c96b-09ad-4fe8-90fe-4e91deedd752","87df8b17-dc27-449b-ba9a-eb084958bb91","f002f58a-df0c-4b5f-ac12-0689871af0e3","40f7c811-c40f-40df-becd-92c5ef4bf359","slideshow_TLgpib","04fbdf0e-5386-4930-b05f-10d6e52f33bf","slid